items.name: NightSentinel
items.description: NightSentinel is a modular Python framework for advanced reconnaissance & data collection. It streamlines web scraping, metadata extraction, social media intelligence, and dark web exploration into one toolkit. Designed for investigators & cybersecurity pros, it flexibly aggregates & analyzes diverse open source data.
